XXXX ZERO uses many of the same quality ingredients as the rest of the XXXX family, such as premium Australian barley, malted in Queensland.

To give XXXX ZERO the perfect crisp finish, we've used Nelson Sauvin hops which gives a slight aroma, making it perfect for all occasions.
